Acceleration Corp said it sold a24.9 pct stake in the common stock of &lt;United Coasts Corp> tothe &lt;Sheet Metal Workers' National Pension Fund>.    The company said it agreed to sell the fund an additional5.1 pct of Hartford, Conn.-based United when the fund receivesapproval from the director of insurance of the state ofArizona.   The company said today's sale reduced its holdings in Unitedto 25 pct. The second sale, when completed, will lower itsstake to 19.9 pct, Acceleration said.    The company said the proceeds from both sales will beroughly equal to the 3,330,000 dlrs it originally invested inUnited Coasts in late 1985 even though it will retain a 19.9pct stake.    Acceleration said it plans to include gains from the stocksales in its results for the first and second quarters of 1987. Reuter&#3;